        <h3>About Us</h3>
        <p>South Dublin County Partnership.</p>
        <p>This website was commissioned by SDC Partnership as one component of an overall initiative to promote progression to third level education in areas where the current take up rate is low.</p>
        <p>As part of an overall strategy to achieve this goal, we believe by targetting children at a younger age to make them aware of the opportunities available to them, it will help them make the right subject choices at secondary level education.</p>
        <img src="~/images/sdcpLogo.png" width="220" height="190" alt="SDCP Logo" />
